snippet.title: Blood of Heroes - Open Beta Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Blood of Heroes is a fierce free-to-play PVP melee action multiplayer game set in a dark fantasy world. Going into Open Beta on August 26th, 2021, make sure to sign up for it now: https://bloodofheroes.online/.

Let’s fight and have fun together!
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bloodofheroesgame
Join us on VK:https://vk.com/bloodofheroes
Follow us on Twitter:
[EN] https://twitter.com/BloodofHeroesEN
[RU] https://twitter.com/BloodofHeroesRU

#BloodOfHeroes #BoH_obt #BoH_gameplay
